00:14:47,574 --> 00:14:48,950
[chuckles]

295
00:14:50,368 --> 00:14:51,786
I should've known.

296
00:14:52,370 --> 00:14:54,497
I'm no match for Mr. Sakamoto.

297
00:15:01,087 --> 00:15:03,006
