427
00:20:20,573 --> 00:20:22,283
He must've put it there yesterday!

428
00:20:23,201 --> 00:20:24,827
He hasn't let his guard down.

429
00:20:26,079 --> 00:20:27,497
Mr. Sakamoto.

430
00:20:27,580 --> 00:20:29,499
