469
00:21:55,626 --> 00:21:56,878
[Sakamoto] Mmm.

470
00:21:58,755 --> 00:22:00,673
[slurps, gulps]

471
00:22:01,632 --> 00:22:03,092
[children laughing]

472
00:22:03,176 --> 00:22:04,761
[girl] Come on, hurry up!

473
00:22:04,844 --> 00:22:06,471
- [bells chime]
